    "body": "This changes the following log message from WARNING to DEBUG.\n\n  WARNING 08-27 07:58:39 [topk_topp_sampler.py:100]\n    FlashInfer 0.2.3+ does not support per-request generators.\n    Falling back to PyTorch-native implementation.\n\nSince this is the code working as intended and there is nothing a user\ncan do with the information, it seems better to keep it as DEBUG level\ninformation.\n\nI made this change after seeing a question from someone about how to\nget the message to go away.\n\nSigned-off-by: Russell Bryant <rbryant@redhat.com>\n",
